                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230409-37-off194 t18230409-37-cd195"></join>, a canvas bag, value 2 d.; six sovereigns, a promisory note for payment of and value 100 l.; a warrant for payment of and value 35 l. 5 s.; and another warrant, for payment of and value 20 l., and a 5 l. Bank note
